missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:27:The mission context is stronger than "the candidate uses an exact NS-looking feature." Tao's result blocks anything resting only on energy identity plus standard harmonic analysis. So the chain should demand a concrete statement of what the averaged model destroys and where that destruction enters the estimate. As written, a candidate can survive Step 1 by sounding algebraically special without showing that the specialness survives localization and actually matters quantitatively.
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:82:The mission is right to require Tao sensitivity. But "destroyed by averaging" is only a necessary discriminator, not a positive mechanism. A quantity can be genuinely NS-specific and still be analytically powerless. The chain sometimes sounds as if Tao sensitivity itself is a form of leverage.
