missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:41:This is also where the chain quietly assumes that a harmonic estimate can be "non-De-Giorgi" while still proving something Tao-relevant. That is not convincing. If the gain uses only elliptic regularity of a harmonic tail, it is almost certainly available in averaged NS too.
