missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/attacks/chain-02.md:26:- The filter "reject anything Tao's averaged model plausibly preserves" is not a reliable research criterion. A lever can fail in the averaged model for irrelevant reasons, or survive averaging and still be exactly the right tool for real NS.
